			<h3 style="text-align:center">3. Eleceed</h3>
			<p>From the author of Noblesse, this manhwa focuses on the adventures of a cat-loving boy, Seo Jisoo who is fast (and I mean really fast) and, you guessed it (no you didn’t), a talking cat. Kayden, a man with the ability to transform and use electricity, turns into a stray cat when he is injured. As fate would have it, Kayden’s the talking cat. Read this story to find out why Kayden was injured, how Jisoo adjusts to his powers and what the biggest mess this dynamic duo can get themselves into.</p>
			<p>Why is it popular? It’s pretty simple. It has a new story concept, some top-tier comedy and most importantly, cats!!!</p>
